                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "puwkY",
                      "name": "P2",
                      "fill": "#4B5563",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Atlanta has quietly gone 7-3 over their last ten games at home, and Sale has been more consistent in his past two starts. The Braves rank 8th in the NL in on-base percentage and have covered the run line 52% of the time when posting a home underdog price of +115 or better. Their bullpen, led by A.J. Minter, holds a 3.12 ERA in save situations.",
